<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694242>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Male genitalia of Siberian Ennominae. A, D—Plagodis dolabraria; B, E—P. pulveraria; C, F—Pseudopanthera macularia; G, J—Epione vespertaria; H, K—E. repandaria; I, L—Opisthograptis luteolata; M–O—Apeira syringaria; P, Q— Ennomos autumnaria. A–C, G–I, M, P—genital segment; D–F, J–L, N, O, Q—phallos. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4694242/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694290>
    dc:description "FIGURE 33. Female genitalia of Siberian Ennominae. A—Plagodis dolabraria; B—P. pulveraria; C—Pseudopanthera macularia; D—Epione vespertaria; E—E. repandaria; F—Opisthograptis luteolata; G—Apeira syringaria; H—Ennomos autumnaria. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4694290/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

